        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         Cast Zefer's, everyone in your group gets some HP over time. While Zefer's is ticking, you cannot cast Shadowbond on any of your group members. But... You can cast it on anyone not in your group. That person gets the full healing, but because you have Zefer's on yourself, you do not take the negative HP from the Shadowbond. Basically, you are healing 500HP over time, for 1 mana, and not taking any damage. Good deal.</P><P>Lots of other ways to cancel out the negative effects of Pact of Shadow or Shadowbond while still getting all the healing on a target. </P><P>Not any more though. </P><P>Cheers,<BR>Ancagalon the Black<BR>Warlock - Terris Thule</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
